title: Nanopackaging - Nanotechnologies and Electronics Packaging
description:
Nanopackaging - Nanotechnologies and Electronics Packaging - James E. Morris (Springer, 2008).pdf

Nanotechnologies are being applied to microelectronics packaging, primarily in the applications of nanoparticle nanocomposites, or in the exploitation of the superior mechanical, electrical, or thermal properties of carbon nanotubes. It will survey the application of nanotechnologies to electronics packaging, as represented by current research across the field
